OL,3,CHow much is Bridget Jones' fictional
OL,4,Cflat worth?
OL,6,FBridget Jones's fictional flat could
OL,7,Fhave nearly tripled in price since the
OL,8,Ffirst film depicting the character was
OL,9,Freleased in 2001, according to
OL,10,Fcalculations by a property website.
OL,12,FRightmove found the average asking
OL,13,Fprice for a one-bedroom flat in
OL,14,FBorough, London, the heart of
OL,15,FBridget's romantic escapades, has
OL,16,Fjumped by 195%.
