OL,3,CHow much is Bridget Jones' fictional
OL,4,Cflat worth?
OL,6,FBack in 2001, when Bridget, played by
OL,7,FRenee Zellweger, was navigating her
OL,8,Fdiary entries and disastrous dates,
OL,9,Fthe average price tag on a one-bedroom
OL,10,Fflat in Borough was #186,150.
OL,12,FIn 2025, as fans await the release of
OL,13,FBridget Jones: Mad About the Boy, a
OL,14,Fone-bed flat in Borough is now priced
OL,15,Fat #549,143.
OL,17,FBy comparison, the average price tag
OL,18,Ffor a typical first-time buyer
OL,19,Fproperty across Britain has increased
OL,20,Fby 155% over the same period, from
OL,21,F#89,207 in 2001 to #227,212 in 2025.
