OL,3,CHow much is Bridget Jones' fictional
OL,4,Cflat worth?
OL,6,FSteve Pimblett, chief data officer at
OL,7,FRightmove, said: "Long-spanning
OL,8,Ffranchises like Bridget Jones are a
OL,9,Freminder just how much things have
OL,10,Fchanged over the years, including
OL,11,Fproperty prices.
OL,13,F"While Bridget may be portrayed as not
OL,14,Falways having it quite together,
OL,15,Flooking back, a one-bedroom flat in
OL,16,Fthe heart of London was a real
OL,17,Fachievement."
